Federated Learning Physical AI Oncology Trials Unification
===========================================================
LaTeX Source Code

Author: Kevin Kawchak, CEO ChemicalQDevice
ORCID:  https://orcid.org/0009-0007-5457-8667
Email:  kevink@chemicalqdevice.com
Date:   February 27, 2026
DOI:    10.5281/zenodo.18795507

Files
-----
  main.tex        - Main LaTeX source file
  arxiv.sty       - Modified arxiv style (removed "A Preprint" header and box frames)
  references.bib  - BibTeX bibliography with 26 references
  README          - This file

Compilation
-----------
  pdflatex main.tex
  bibtex main
  pdflatex main.tex
  pdflatex main.tex

Requirements
------------
  - TeX Live 2023 or later
  - Packages: hyperref, booktabs, amsfonts, amsmath, graphicx, enumitem,
    listings, xcolor, longtable, array, multirow, tabularx, float, tikz

Style Modifications
-------------------
  The arxiv.sty file is based on kourgeorge/arxiv-style with two modifications:
  1. Removed "A Preprint" from page headers and under-title text
  2. Removed horizontal rule box frames around the title

